      <title>勒庞重燃预算协议希望，法国债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/french-bonds-outperform-as-le-pen-revives-hopes-of-budget-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者希望法国能够比许多投资者预期的更快结束持续数月的政府财政政治争论，法国债券延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/french-bonds-outperform-as-le-pen-revives-hopes-of-budget-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国每周申请失业救济人数超过预期，达到 224,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/us-weekly-jobless-claims-jump-above-estimates-to-224-000-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，美国失业救济申请人数意外增加 9,000 人，达到 224,000 人，而持续申领失业救济人数则下降至 187 万人。迈克尔·麦基对这些数字进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/us-weekly-jobless-claims-jump-above-estimates-to-224-000-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:03:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果马克龙放宽债务路径，勒庞将在未来几周内公布法国预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/le-pen-france-budget-likely-within-weeks-if-macron-eases-debt-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞表示，只要下一任总理准备以更慢的速度缩小赤字，法国就能克服政府垮台并在“几周内”出台预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/le-pen-france-budget-likely-within-weeks-if-macron-eases-debt-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 13:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及镑自三月以来首次贬值，跌破里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/egypt-pound-weakens-past-50-a-dollar-for-first-time-since-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及镑兑美元汇率自 3 月份贬值以来首次跌破 50，这是一个备受关注的里程碑，因为这个北非国家承诺实施浮动汇率制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/egypt-pound-weakens-past-50-a-dollar-for-first-time-since-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
